item.description:
Topsfield BNI, a professional networking organization, invites anyone interested in a fun, social evening of business networking to join us in celebrating Cinco de Mayo at Supino's Restaurant, 250 Newbury Street, Danvers, MA, May 5th at 6:30 p.m.

BNI, Business Networking International, is the world's largest networking organization and members benefit from sharing ideas, information and most importantly, business referrals. May 5th promises to be an excellent opportunity to meet other professionals interested in collaborative networking. Bring plenty of business cards!
item.how_to_find_us: Ask for the BNI Meeting. We have a private room for this event.
item.name: Topsfield BNI Social Networking Night May Meetup
